21#include <stdio.h> /* for MPC_ASSERT */
22#include <float.h> /* for LDBL_MANT_DIG */
23#include "mpc-impl.h"
24
25int
26mpc_pow_ld (mpc_ptr z, mpc_srcptr x, long double y, mpc_rnd_t rnd)
27{
28 mpc_t yy;
29 int inex;
30
31 MPC_ASSERT(FLT_RADIX == 2);
32 mpc_init3 (yy, LDBL_MANT_DIG, MPFR_PREC_MIN);
33 mpc_set_ld (yy, y, MPC_RNDNN); /* exact */
34 inex = mpc_pow (z, x, yy, rnd);
35 mpc_clear (yy);
36 return inex;
37}
